sequenceDiagram
    participant "AI Processing Worker" as AIProcessingWorker
    participant "RabbitMQ Broker" as RabbitMQBroker
    participant "AWS Monitoring & Alerting" as AWSMonitoringAlerting
    participant "Operator" as Operator

    activate AIProcessingWorker
    RabbitMQBroker->>AIProcessingWorker: 1. AMQP basic.deliver (SowUploadedEvent, deliveryTag, redelivered=true)
    AIProcessingWorker->>AIProcessingWorker: 2. Process message: Catch non-transient Exception (e.g., InvalidSowFileFormatException)
    AIProcessingWorker->>AIProcessingWorker: 2.1. Update SOW status in DB to 'Failed'
    AIProcessingWorker-->>AIProcessingWorker: Commit successful
    AIProcessingWorker->>AWSMonitoringAlerting: 2.2. Log permanent failure event with Correlation ID
    activate RabbitMQBroker
    AIProcessingWorker->>RabbitMQBroker: 3. AMQP basic.nack (deliveryTag, requeue=false)
    RabbitMQBroker->>RabbitMQBroker: 4. Route message to Dead-Letter Exchange (DLX)
    RabbitMQBroker-->>RabbitMQBroker: Route to 'sow-processing-dlq'
    AWSMonitoringAlerting->>AWSMonitoringAlerting: 5. Monitor DLQ metric (ApproximateNumberOfMessagesVisible)
    AWSMonitoringAlerting->>AWSMonitoringAlerting: 6. CloudWatch Alarm state transitions to ALARM
    AWSMonitoringAlerting-->>AWSMonitoringAlerting: Trigger SNS Action
    AWSMonitoringAlerting->>Operator: 7. Publish SNS notification to alert endpoint (e.g., PagerDuty, Slack)
    Operator->>AWSMonitoringAlerting: 8. Investigate: Query CloudWatch Logs using Correlation ID from alert
    AWSMonitoringAlerting-->>Operator: Log stream with error details
    Operator->>RabbitMQBroker: 9. Investigate: Inspect message contents in DLQ
    RabbitMQBroker-->>Operator: Message payload and headers
    Operator->>RabbitMQBroker: 10. Resolve: Manually re-queue or discard message
    RabbitMQBroker-->>Operator: Action confirmation

    note over RabbitMQBroker: The 'sow-processing-queue' in RabbitMQ must be configured with 'x-dead-letter-exchange' pointing ...
    note over Operator: Operator's investigation is guided by a runbook that details how to interpret log messages, commo...

    deactivate RabbitMQBroker
    deactivate AIProcessingWorker
